(define/contract (min-sum nums1 nums2)
  (-> (listof exact-integer?) (listof exact-integer?) exact-integer?)
  (let* ([sum1 (apply + (filter positive? nums1))]
         [sum2 (apply + (filter positive? nums2))]
         [zeros1 (count zero? nums1)]
         [zeros2 (count zero? nums2)]
         [total-zeros (+ zeros1 zeros2)])
    (if (and (= zeros1 0) (= zeros2 0) (not (= sum1 sum2)))
        -1
        (let ([min-sum (if (> sum1 sum2)
                           (+ sum1 (* (- total-zeros (if (> sum2 sum1) 1 0)) 1))
                           (+ sum2 (* (- total-zeros (if (> sum1 sum2) 1 0)) 1)))])
          (if (or (> sum1 sum2) (> sum2 sum1))
              (if (= (modulo (- (max sum1 sum2) (min sum1 sum2)) (- total-zeros (if (> sum1 sum2) 1 0))) 0)
                  min-sum
                  (+ min-sum (- (- total-zeros (if (> sum1 sum2) 1 0)) (modulo (- (max sum1 sum2) (min sum1 sum2)) (- total-zeros (if (> sum1 sum2) 1 0))))))
              (+ (max sum1 sum2) total-zeros))))))
